            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "3 in 1 SMALL EDC POCKET KNIFE: Featuring a nail file, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure; great for camping and every day carry on your key ring",
