                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COMPACT DESIGN: Small pocket knife is just 2.25 inches overall when closed; super lightweight you'll never sacrifice on space or weight",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "TASK READY: Whether you’re fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife is a great holiday gift idea for mens stocking stuffers",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "KEYCHAIN POCKET KNIFE: With an included keychain ring incorporated into the design, you can attach the mini pocket knife multitool to just about anything you need: backpack, camping gear, keys and much more",
